	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I just improved my 400+ color palette demo to not shake (well, it shakes by two pixels, but at 30 Hz, so it's much less noticeable). Cleaner, easier-to-follow code is included, rather than the super-optimized code like in the previous version. NTSC-only at the moment:
<br />
<br /><a href="http://blargg.parodius.com/nes-code/full_palette.zip" class="postlink">full_palette.zip</a>
<br />
<br /><img src="http://blargg.parodius.com/nes-code/full_palette.jpg" alt="Image" /> <img src="http://blargg.parodius.com/nes-code/full_palette_smooth.jpg" alt="Image" />

		

		</td>
